    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281112</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>レスター博士が、
あんな人なんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I would have never imagined the renowned
Lester would be that kind of jerk... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、他にあてがないんだかラ。
さっき自分で言ったじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But we can't rely on anyone else. This won't
be the last time we have to deal with him. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、だけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...you're right, but... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_008Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おや、&lt;Klarth&gt;に客人か？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh hey, are you here to visit &lt;Klarth&gt;? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_009Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>浮かない顔だな。
難癖つけられて、
追っ払われたってとこか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He isn't a very cheerful person. Yet, you shouldn't
blame him or drive him away like that easily. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい、あの……わたしたち、
精霊のことで&lt;Klarth&gt;さんに
相談があって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, you see...we came here since we
heard &lt;Klarth&gt; would know something
about Summon Spirits and...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>281956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんた、誰？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And just who do you think you are? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282044</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと、&lt;Dio&gt;、
失礼でしょ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hold on, &lt;Dio&gt;, that's impolite.... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_013Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕はあの男の友人だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm that guy's friend. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_014Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こちらこそ、友人が
失礼したね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I should be the one saying you're impolite to my friend. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_015Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……本当は、
あんなヤツじゃないんだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...As a matter of fact, he isn't such
a bad person most of the time... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_017Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>学会の幹部連中に、目の前で
召喚術の論文を燃やされた
頃からずっとあんな調子だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A bunch of guys from the most privileged
colleges burnt his Summoning thesis in front
of everyone. It's no wonder he's furious. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282496</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひどい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How could they be so cruel...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_019Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>学会の連中は、精霊の存在なんて
眉唾もんだって思ってるからね。
これ見よがしに論文を燃やして……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Those academic hypocrites did so to regard the
Summon Spirits' existence as scientifically fake.
He was the first to see his thesis burning... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_020Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ミラルドが出て行ってからは
もっとひどくなっていった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shortly after that Milard left him
and he's been getting worse since. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_021Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……僕が同じ仕打ちを受けたら……
我慢できないだろうな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If I received the same treatment
he did...I'd be crushed... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_022Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ところで、&lt;Klarth&gt;に何を
相談したいんだい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Anyways, what did you want to ask &lt;Klarth&gt;? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>282908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_023Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>僕でも力になれることは
ないかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's just a guess but...you wouldn't happen to be
searching for the Spirit's powers, would you? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリートってヤツの
いる洞窟へ行くんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We were going to Efreet-whatever or other-'s cavern. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_025Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>イフリートだって！！
君たちだけで行くつもりかい？
あそこは迷いやすいし、危険だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet, you say!? Are you guys truly planning to
travel there!? It's very easy to lose one's way
there! You must proceed with utmost care! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283228</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_026Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、これをあげよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you insist, you can have this. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ど、どうしてこれを？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why are you helping us? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_028Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちみたいな
子どもだけでは危険だろ。
だからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't just sit and watch some children
go off to such a dangerous place and
not do anything. That's why. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283492</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_029Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当は、僕が付いていってあげたい
んだけど……予定があってね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I could go with you instead of just
giving that but...I have plans already. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_030Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>水の力を宿しているこの剣なら
イフリートのいる&lt;Red&gt;熱砂の洞窟&lt;White&gt;の
魔物には効果があるはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The power of water lies within that sword
and is effective against the monsters lurking
in Efreet's Cavern of Burning Sand. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_031Z&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さて、僕はあいつの顔でも
見てくるよ。じゃあね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now then, I'll go take a look at
&lt;Klarth&gt; myself. See you! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、だからって
&lt;Klarth&gt;さんのあんな言い方……
ないと、思う……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But if what he said is true then we don't
need do what &lt;Klarth&gt; said... I think... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>283920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、イフリート
連れてこようぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Let's lead the way to Efreet! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>精霊連れてったら、レスター博士、
元気づけられっかもしんねー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If we find that Summon Spirit, I'm sure
the renowned Lester  will be back
in top shape! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、かな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're....right... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どっちにしろ、精霊の力が
必要だったんだしさ、
ついでついで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We do have to get the Spirit's power at all costs, anyways, 
so this plays fair for us. We'll get to it, no problem! </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Jank</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルールル！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuruururu! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね……うん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I agree, yeah! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284568</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;熱砂の洞窟&lt;White&gt;の
イフリート、だっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Efreet's Cavern of Burning Sand, was it? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284568</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>粗暴で丸焦げにしちゃう
って言ってたけド……
気をつけないと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He told us pretty harshly that we'd get
completely cremated...please be careful...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらには
『なりきり士』の力が
あんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All's good though, since we have
the power of Roleplayers!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>284716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_040_030_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>全然だいじょーぶだって。
行こーぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It;ll be no problem at all, let's go! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
